OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772467871
OL,3,CSuspected drone strike hits RAF base
OL,4,Cin Cyprus
OL,6,FA suspected drone strike hit RAF
OL,7,FAkrotiri in Cyprus, the Ministry of
OL,8,FDefence (MoD) has confirmed.
OL,10,FThere were no casualties in the
OL,11,Fincident at the base near Limassol.
OL,13,FAn MoD spokesperson said: "Our armed
OL,14,Fforces are responding to a suspected
OL,15,Fdrone strike at RAF Akrotiri in Cyprus
OL,16,Fat midnight local time.
OL,18,F"Our force protection in the region is
OL,19,Fat the highest level and the base has
OL,20,Fresponded to defend our people.
OL,26,@uD@[OUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
