CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772467871
OL,3,CSuspected drone strike hits RAF base
OL,4,Cin Cyprus
OL,6,F"This is a live situation and further
OL,7,Finformation will be provided in due
OL,8,Fcourse."
OL,10,FAccording to the MoD's website, the
OL,11,Fjoint operating base is "used as a
OL,12,Fforward mounting base for overseas
OL,13,Foperations in the Middle East and for
OL,14,Ffast jet training".
OL,16,FIt is understood the UK Government
OL,17,Frecently moved additional resources to
OL,18,Fbases in Cyprus as part of ongoing
OL,19,Foperations in the Middle East.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@HO]sD@YOUvD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
